# CLIClaw Tracker

Real-time multi-agent coordination dashboard built with SvelteKit.

## Quick Start

```bash
cd tracker
npm install
npm run dev
```

Open http://localhost:9122

## Features

- **Messages**: View agent-to-agent communication
- **Tasks**: Track task status across agents
- **Tokens**: Monitor token usage per agent
- **Agents**: See active agents and their activity

## API Endpoints

- `GET /api/events` - All tracker events
- `GET /api/messages` - Message events only
- `GET /api/tasks` - Task events only
- `GET /api/tokens` - Token usage events
- `GET /api/agents` - List of active agents

## Development

```bash
npm run dev      # Start dev server on port 9122
npm run build    # Build for production
npm run preview  # Preview production build
```

## Data Source

Reads from `../.cliclaw/tracker.jsonl` and auto-refreshes every 2 seconds.
